headline: Buybacks Hit Record in First Half of Year. These Stocks Are Benefiting the Most.
summary: A Goldman Sachs report shows that companies that have been more aggressive purchasers of their own shares, do better than the broader market.

headline: 1 Volatile Stock with Exciting Potential and 2 We Find Risky
summary: Volatility cuts both ways - while it creates opportunities, it also increases risk, making sharp declines just as likely as big gains. This unpredictability can shake out even the most experienced investors.
